{"ts": "2026-06-09T18:02:16.558876+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "The repository token appears to have read-only access, so I cannot write comments or labels directly. However, here is my triage assessment:\n\n---\n\n## Triage Assessment for Issue #1\n\n**Title:** `apply_migrations.sh` applies files in wrong order on filesystems with case-folding\n\n**Verdict: ✅ Valid Bug — Should remain open and be fixed**\n\n### Evidence\n\nI reviewed the relevant source files:\n\n1. **`scripts/apply_migrations.sh`** — Uses a bare shell glob loop:\n   ```bash\n   for f in migrations/*.sql; do\n   ```\n   This relies on locale-dependent glob ordering (governed by `LC_COLLATE`), which can differ across macOS (APFS case-insensitive) and Linux distributions.\n\n2. **`migrations/`** contains three files with strict dependency ordering:\n   - `001_create_users.sql` → creates `users` table\n   - `002_create_sessions.sql` → creates `sessions` table with `REFERENCES users(id)`\n   - `003_add_session_index.sql` → creates an index on `sessions(user_id)`\n\n   If `003` runs before `002`, PostgreSQL will report `relation \"sessions\" does not exist`. If `002` runs before `001`, it reports `relation \"users\" does not exist`. Both failure modes are reported.\n\n3. **Two independent reporters** confirm the issue on both macOS (APFS, zsh) and Linux (Ubuntu 22.04, bash, ext4), ruling out a single-platform quirk.\n\n### Recommended Action\n\nThe fix is straightforward — replace the bare glob with an explicit sort, e.g.:\n```bash\nfor f in $(ls migrations/*.sql | sort); do\n```\nor even better, using `LC_ALL=C sort` to guarantee numeric-safe ordering regardless of locale.\n\n**Suggested labels:** `bug`, `priority/high`\n\nThe issue is valid, well-documented, and has a clear path to resolution. It should remain open and be addressed.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 469, "prompt_tokens": 10727, "total_tokens": 11196, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 34, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 10496}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "mimo-v2.5-pro", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "4af23e603e41455aacbf55c28051fe2d", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ead8c-6695-7cd2-a06d-8939ea7c2f4e-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 10727, "output_tokens": 469, "total_tokens": 11196, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 10496}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 34}}}}]}}}
